            </span>
          </td>
          <td>ðŸ˜­</td>
          <td>Initial commits. We got there, but ChatGPT is HORRIBLE at sprite sheets. I've lost so much time to having it try to handle pixel art and it crashed/hit its limits. More later. I want to hire a pixel artist once stable, but am using ChatGPT to mock.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Import Comic Neue at the top */
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Comic+Neue:wght@400;700&display=swap');

  /* Header styling with Comic Sans-inspired font stack */
  .header-container {
    font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', 'Comic Neue', 'Chalkboard SE', cursive, sans-serif;
    font-size: min(8vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background-image: linear-gradient(to right, red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, violet);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center; /* Changed from 'left' to 'center' */
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 0;
  }

  /* Table styling for Changelog */
  .changelog-table {
    margin: 20px auto;
    border-collapse: separate;
    border-spacing: 0;
    width: 90%;
  }

  /* Pill row styling for header and data rows */
  .pill-row th,
  .pill-row td {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    /* Remove default borders so the row appears as a single pill */
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    color: #fff;
  }

  /* Header row: lighter brown pill */
  .changelog-table thead .pill-row {
    background-color: #4CAF50; /* Sienna */
  }

  /* Data row: darker brown pill (simulate older post) */
  .changelog-table tbody .pill-row.old {
    background-color: #CD853F; /* SaddleBrown */
  }

  /* Make entire row a pill with rounded corners (apply to first and last cells) */
  .changelog-table thead .pill-row th:first-child {
    border-top-left-radius: 9999px;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 9999px;
  }
  .changelog-table thead .pill-row th:last-child {
    border-top-right-radius: 9999px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 9999px;
  }
  .changelog-table tbody .pill-row.old td:first-child {
    border-top-left-radius: 9999px;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 9999px;
  }
  .changelog-table tbody .pill-row.old td:last-child {
    border-top-right-radius: 9999px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 9999px;
  }

  /* Styling for the date cell */
  .date-cell {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: left;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .calendar-icon {
    margin-right: 5px;
  }

  /* Ensure the contents of the changelog data rows are left aligned */
  .changelog-table tbody .pill-row.old td {
    text-align: left;
  }
</style>
